sentences.english: Blessed are those who give thanks.
sentences.chinese: 懂得感恩的人總是被佑護。

sentences.english: Washed by the rivers, blest by suns of home.
sentences.chinese: 受着河水的沐浴，受着家鄉陽光的佑護。

sentences.english: China is a symbol of peace, meanwhile it owns the absolute power to uphold peace.
sentences.chinese: 中國是和平的象徵，同時也是佑護和平的絕對力量。

sentences.english: Meet adoration to my household gods.
sentences.chinese: 並對我家的佑護神表示崇敬。
而佑護之“神靈”正是科舉自身。
